{"tid":27640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我另一半成日質隻臭腳比我食","createTime":"2016-12-07T12:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T03:49:59.000Z","uid":50286,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"208fcc45c8c82f03c942bb88861ca9776fc44156","tid":27640,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"佢返工成日著埋d婆仔鞋，<br />\n<br />\n一兩個鐘就會出腳汗老泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD腳汗酸酸叔叔咁經過朝九晚五既洗禮，<br />\n<br />\n個陣除真係好恐怖！好恐怖！<br />\n<br />\n有時落雨佢踩過水tum，個陣酸叔味仲會昇華，好似混入左渠水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻腳係灰色架！！！<br />\n<br />\n每日放工佢返到黎都會叫我用口幫佢除左對婆仔鞋，一隻一隻腳指咁啜到乾乾淨淨，跟住再含住佢地三十秒，然後由腳面奶到腳底。<br />\n<br />\n如果我閉氣佢會話：你係唔係嫌我隻腳臭？你係唔係唔愛我啦？<br />\n<br />\n跟住仲對隻腳落我個鼻到迫我聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我真係好想嘔，真係好撚臭，但係我一作嘔佢就會用腳實住我個口，我連嘔都嘔唔到。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴絲請問有咩止嘔丸推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181a3c803a4c48bd6e8047c8056015b9b4d10f00","tid":27640,"uid":7463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3066a3705812517c1a83984153b4730baf8339","tid":27640,"uid":7463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"幾好笑wow"},{"pid":"eaac9194e7b4b84c0ea1e40839e11852ba4dfa1e","tid":27640,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"好地地聞自己隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ad031d12527bb6f713cd897f9a87b00757b357","tid":27640,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cacab553032a9